scripts.cy:run: npm run clean && npx cypress run
scripts.cy:run:chrome: npm run clean && npx cypress run --browser chrome
scripts.cy:run:edge: npm run clean && npx cypress run --browser edge
scripts.cy:run:firefox: npm run clean && npx cypress run --browser firefox
scripts.cy:parallel: npm run clean && cypress-parallel -s cy:run -t 4 -d cypress/e2e/**/*.js
scripts.cy:parallel:chrome: npm run clean && cypress-parallel -s cy:run:chrome -t 4 -d cypress/e2e/**/*.js
scripts.cy:parallel:edge: npm run clean && cypress-parallel -s cy:run:edge -t 4 -d cypress/e2e/**/*.js
scripts.cy:parallel:firefox: npm run clean && cypress-parallel -s cy:run:firefox -t 4 -d cypress/e2e/**/*.js
scripts.cy:test:cherrypick: npm run clean && npx cypress run --browser chrome --spec "cypress/e2e/LoginTubeIQ_test.js"
